So we created a splash screen, which also allowed us to create the navigation to be able to navigate

00:26.380 --> 00:27.190
between screens.

00:27.730 --> 00:34.540
And then we worked on our main screen, so there were different parts that we had to work on, such

00:34.540 --> 00:35.950
as the App Bar at the top.

