01:32.590 --> 01:35.770
will customize the top bar even further.

01:36.100 --> 01:41.050
And you should always think in those terms, especially when you put together these composable functions,

01:41.050 --> 01:45.510
because the idea is to have reusable code in this case, reusable, composable.

